quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,Naye nga omufu teyasaddaaka wadde okusaala
  75,32,Wabula yalimbisa ebigambo bya Katonda nabyesamba
  75,33,Olwo nno naatambula nadda eri abantu be nga yeeraga
  75,34,(Aligambibwa nti ekyo) ekikutuuseeko kikugwanidde era ddala kikugwanidde (owange ggwe omwonoonyi)
  75,35,Ate era kikugwanidde ng'ate era ddala kikugwanidde
  75,36,Omuntu alowooza nti ayinza okulekwa neyeeyisa nga bwayagala
  75,37,Tajjukira nti yasooka kuba tondo lyamazzi agazaala agateekebwa mu nabaana
  75,38,"Oluvanyuma naafuuka ekisayisayi, olwo Katonda naamutonda namussaako byonna ebimufuula omuntu"
  75,39,"Nga bwatyo bwakola emitendera ebiri, omusajja n'omukazi"
  75,40,Abaffe oyo eyakola omuntu mu ngeri eyo tasobola kulamusa bafu